Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}汝等終於來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}來呀快放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}師父快到定期報告會的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}已經到這個時候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}下次可以隨時再來挑戰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}師父您和那些來拜師的人切磋的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}究竟在看什麼東西呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}鳳凰星武祭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}虎峰剛才那場比賽有個很有意思的小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好像是星導館的一個叫天霧的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}作為一個可造之材來說那小子真是出類拔萃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真希望他現在就來我們這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就算您這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過他的力量似乎受到了限制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這一點不是也很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我記得宋和羅下一場就要對上他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是讓人羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來您在這裏啊師父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}趙師姐也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是你們這對雙胞胎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沈雲還有沈華
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的因為我們很有可能在第六輪碰上宋師兄他們那一組
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們水派和他們木派向來不怎麼對付
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}一旦交戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}下手說不定會有點重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以想先知會師父一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們兩個...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}隨你們便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老身的目的不過是傳授你們武藝罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}並沒有興趣教什麼大道理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}師父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不愧是繼承「萬有天羅」之人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是胸襟寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}弟子深感佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過真的會如你們想得那般順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}您的意思是...我們的實力不如宋師兄他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只是明天的比賽宋和羅能否勝出還尚未可知吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難道師父您認為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}宋和羅還會敗下陣來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只要比賽精彩老身就心滿意足了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為此老身才會來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果天霧他們能贏得明天那場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那想必他一定能繼續拓寬自己的器量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老身非常期待這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為那樣發展
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}才更有趣不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}才一天時間竟然就傳播得這麼廣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}出場選手那邊肯定得到了更加詳細的資料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你覺得我們的秘密暴露了多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}總之和依蕾奈她們比完之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}大致的限制時間應該已經暴露了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我也覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}問題窄於你解放能力存在副作用的這一點也暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}夭霧選手為了回復因解放的副作用而導致的肉體損害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}需要一定的時間來緩和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這條情報似乎是出自雷渥夫那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可惡的惡辣之王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼你身體的實際情況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還行雖然依舊有點痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但應付一般的戰鬥應該沒有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}果然還是無法發揮全力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個就有點困難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼我需要確認兩點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在沒有解除封印的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你為什麼能具備一定程度的防禦能力呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}防禦的話有些方面是可以用經驗和預判來應付的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此那麼另外一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}僅僅一瞬間解放力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個技巧你現在這個狀態能夠使用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想應該能夠用一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}下一場對戰的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是界龍序列第二十位和第二十三位的一對組合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他們是界龍的學生會長「萬有天羅」的嫡傳弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是精通近戰的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果你是萬全狀態的話應該不難取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但你現在這種情況老實說負擔有些大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果只是 1 對 1 的話我也不會落於下風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但要同時對付兩個人的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因此我現在有一個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你有什麼對策嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}終於來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}鳳凰星武祭第五輪最後一場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}贏得八強最後一個席位的究竟會是哪一組呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}今年這一屆水準相當高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以無論哪一組都有取勝的可能性哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼我來向各位介紹一下已經晉級的備受矚目的組合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}首先是本次大賽的頭號種子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}阿爾坎特最新最強的擬形體阿爾迪和莉姆希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}它們兩個是代替艾涅絲妲&卡蜜拉組合參加本次大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}第一輪它們在讓給對手一分鐘進行攻擊後取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是給了大家極大的震撼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}接著是界龍引以為傲的雙子惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}「幻映創起」黎沈雲&「幻映霧散」黎沈華
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他們通過變幻多樣的配合不斷施展出的星僊術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真的是非常難以應對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他們把之前遇到的所有對戰對手都玩弄於股掌之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}最後輕鬆取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}另外還有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}賭上銀翼騎士團的榮耀與名譽而戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘉萊多瓦思學園的多洛提歐· 雷姆斯和艾略特· 佛斯達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}多洛提歐選手是第三次參加鳳凰星武祭的身經百戰的強者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}艾略特選手則是以初中部身份便加入了銀翼騎士團的年輕天才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}「鳳凰星武祭」星導館勢在必得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她們能否將這種氣魄展現到最後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}刀藤綺凜&沙沙宮紗夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}擅長近戰的刀藤選手和用火力壓制對手的沙沙宮選手的配合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是令人為之沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是提到星導館學園的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}接下來即將比賽的天霧&裏斯妃特組合也要重點關注啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}面對擁有純星煌式武裝「霸潰血鐮」的依蕾奈&普莉熙拉組合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他們取得了漂亮的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而在另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有關天霧選手的各種臆測也傳得沸沸揚揚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果那些報道內容屬實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那將是一個巨大的不利因素
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}他是否正在恢復因解放能力而導致的損害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還有我們今天能否再欣賞到他的那種表演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了在各種層面上都備受關注的這場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}星導館學園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}夭霧綾斗尤莉絲· 愛雷克西亞· 馮· 裏斯妃特組合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後是界龍第七學院宋然羅坤展組合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}現在入場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}天霧君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}無論你的坊間傳言的真相究竟如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們都將全力應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老實說我更希望和萬全狀態的你一對一交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但這是規定了必須組合出戰的鳳凰星武祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以你可別怨我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們只是希望能在戰鬥之前先跟你說個明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此不愧是習武之人的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來還有那樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了雙方選手都站上了擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想對方肯定會先試探一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}看看你是否真的無法全力應戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後馬上就能看穿傳聞屬實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好聽仔細了綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這就是「印記」 你一定要記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}暗號就叫「煙火」 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在此之前一定要完成所有條件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}闖過第五輪比賽晉級八強的究竟會是哪一組呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}鳳凰星武祭第五輪第八場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}來也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此看來傳聞是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}華麗綻放吧九輪舞焰花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉綾斗被他擺脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}竟然承受住了剛才那一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個天霧選手竟然被單方面地壓制真是出人意料的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然宋羅組合的連攜技確實是相當精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒有展現之前那種華麗表演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}星辰力的淬煉程度也遠遠不如以往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我看傳聞說的果然是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綻放吧赤壁斷焰華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這是裏斯妃特選手的招數嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}突然出現的火牆將擂台分為了兩塊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此要把我和羅分隔開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣一來就是一對一了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你認為一對一的話自己就有勝算?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老實說我覺得很難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但總不能就這麼放棄吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是我的問題太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒傳聞中那麼厲害嘛華焰魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這種實力才排序列第二十三?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}放在星導館的話毫無疑問能進入「尖子十二人」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}赤熱灼斬花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}維持這堵火牆分散了你的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是也不必用這麼誇張的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}還有很多其它的辦法能營造出一對一的局面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒辦法為了獲勝我們只能出此下策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}聽你的意思是還有後手?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老實說我很佩服你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖說專注於防守
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但沒想到竟然能承受住我那麼多次攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}如果你處於萬全狀態的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我們現在的處境可能就會反一反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不換成是我的話甚至撐不了那麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想應該不至於那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過我也不忍心再讓你承受無謂的痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為了向你表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就讓我用下一擊分出勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你還是快一點吧不然火牆的另一邊可就要分出勝負咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的意思是我的搭檔會落敗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}現在這種狀態的「叢雲」根本敵不過我們沒錯吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}現在這種狀態的綾斗要想戰勝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想應該只能靠出其不意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但我和宋可沒有天真到會露出那樣的破綻給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}另一邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}無論你怎麼防禦都沒用我的這一拳將會粉碎一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我勸你別想著怎麼防禦還是專注閃避為好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}華麗綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}六瓣爆焰花· 二輪開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}校徽破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}比 比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}勝者天霧綾斗&尤莉絲· 愛雷克西亞· 馮· 裏斯妃特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}攻敵不備非常精彩的配合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為我們上演了瞬間逆轉的一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哎呀哎呀其實沒你說的那麼簡單哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的意思是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}剛才宋選手和天霧選手是在進行近戰交鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而羅選手則是應對裏斯妃特選手的遠距離攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}星導館組合通過突然的互換打亂了對手保持的間隔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}從而成功地發動了一次漂亮的突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哎呀真是太精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}姑且是贏下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛能夠撐過今天這一場非常關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只要明天休息一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}下一場比賽你也能發揮出全力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這點倒是不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過尤莉絲你呢傷勢之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}嘛似乎沒有斷掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}重要的是下一場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對手相當棘手就算你能全力發揮似乎也很麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們該不會是來祝賀我們晉級的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}想出那個戰術的人是你吧「華焰魔女」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}必須彼此信賴才能夠做到非常漂亮的配合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}今天我們輸得很徹底
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}相當精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}哪..哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過你們要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那種策略對你們下一場的對手是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只是單純的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你大可放心地聽我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就算你這麼說我們下一場的對手可是你們的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你認為我會相信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就算是同一所學園的人也不見得就是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}黎沈雲黎沈華這兩人和我們水火不容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然不至於會向你們透露他們的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但比起那對雙胞胎我們還是對你們更有好感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以就想過來聲援你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼我重新問一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}策略對他們沒用是什麼意思?
